{"id":666810,"date":[{"year":1984,"month":1,"day":13}],"page":"2","source":"新华社","region":"纽约","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"273","ytitle":"","mtitle":"迎来赵紫阳　侨胞心欢笑","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新华社纽约一月十日电　纽约中文报纸《北美日报》今天刊登了一位名叫万里行的华侨为欢迎赵紫阳总理访问美国而写的一首诗，题为《迎来紫阳心欢笑》。诗文如下:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自四川的山腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自北京金水桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自中国的代表。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们华侨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把您看作忘年交，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看作解冻的日照。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用电视介绍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用买宴席票，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用仔细地瞧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们华侨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中有老赵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"善搏蛟龙拿铁锹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说一说家乡新貌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈一谈统一航道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲一讲中美友好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们华侨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眉开眼齐笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮似海啸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲来培育中美新苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来十亿人民问好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送来一座友谊长桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们华侨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来紫阳心欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿把终身作柳条。"}]}